rows.label: qst610101_msg0002
rows.name:
I work at the Nocclia Timber Site
up by the Gula Divine Beast's
nape, you see.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0003
rows.name:
Day in, day out, we're breakin' our
backs choppin' down trees.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0004
rows.name:
But the other day, I got to work and
noticed a load of them were missing!
Just vanished into thin air.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0005
rows.name:
Even with all of us working together,
we only manage maybe five trees a day.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0006
rows.name:
They're massive, you see, and really
heavy to boot. It's hard, hard work.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0007
rows.name:
So it pisses me right off to think 
someone's just stealin' them!

rows.label: qst610101_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh man, everyone at the site will
be so thrilled to hear that.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0010
rows.name:
Afraid I got nothing when it comes to
the thief, though.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0011
rows.name:
I guess the best place to start would be
askin' round the Timber Site. Someone
might have a lead for you.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0012
rows.name:
I'll head over there later to
hear what you've found out.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0101
rows.name:
I want you to find the scum that's
stealing our wood!

rows.label: qst610101_msg0102
rows.name:
Start by askin' around the
Nocclia Timber Site up by the 
Gula Divine Beast's nape.

rows.label: qst610101_msg0103
rows.name:
I'll head over there later to
hear what you've found out.
